snippet.textDisplay: We give this to our covid pts. I mostly work in the ICU, not the covid floor. (So severity is severe where I most commonly work). It doesn't seem to clinically make a difference in outcomes, but I am always happy for any research that will improve ANY covid symptoms! Thank you!
